[SPEAKER_01] niti ćemo se izjašnjavati,

667
00:33:00,579 --> 00:33:02,680
[SPEAKER_01] da se zalažemo zato da svi ima puno djeca.

668
00:33:02,680 --> 00:33:03,099
[SPEAKER_01] Ma ne.

669
00:33:03,099 --> 00:33:05,200
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to je stvarno pitanje osobnog izbora.

670
00:33:05,200 --> 00:33:05,799
[SPEAKER_01] Tako.

671
00:33:05,799 --> 00:33:08,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ali živimo u vremenu u kojem nije popularno,

672
00:33:08,119 --> 00:33:08,920
[SPEAKER_01] to sam uvodno rekao,

673
00:33:08,920 --> 00:33:10,220
[SPEAKER_01] ima djecu jer je to zahtjevno.

674
00:33:10,220 --> 00:33:12,859
[SPEAKER_01] Zahtjevnije nego prije kagoda se to ne čini tako.

675
00:33:12,859 --> 00:33:14,900
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što su pritisni s puno više strana

676
00:33:14,900 --> 00:33:16,640
[SPEAKER_01] i puno se više očekuje

677
00:33:24,619 --> 00:33:26,180
[SPEAKER_01] kad je bilo sasvim normalno,

678
00:33:26,180 --> 00:33:27,920
[SPEAKER_01] iako su ljudi živjeli u velikoj neimaštini,

679
00:33:27,920 --> 00:33:29,079
[SPEAKER_01] bilo je sasvim normalno

680
00:33:29,079 --> 00:33:31,160
[SPEAKER_01] da imate osmere od desetere od dvanestere od djeca.

681
00:33:31,160 --> 00:33:33,180
[SPEAKER_01] Danas više ne živimo u takim vremenima.

682
00:33:33,180 --> 00:33:34,740
[SPEAKER_01] I zato danas, evo, oni roditelji

683
00:33:34,740 --> 00:33:36,680
[SPEAKER_01] koji su spremni staviti sa strane

684
00:33:36,680 --> 00:33:37,980
[SPEAKER_01] malo svoju poslovnu karijeru,

685
00:33:37,980 --> 00:33:39,400
[SPEAKER_01] ne malo nego i puno često puta

686
00:33:39,400 --> 00:33:40,859
[SPEAKER_01] i mnoge druge komocije

687
00:33:40,859 --> 00:33:42,140
[SPEAKER_01] i žele imati djecu,

688
00:33:42,140 --> 00:33:43,839
[SPEAKER_01] pa super, rajmo i podupiti tome.

689
00:33:43,839 --> 00:33:44,160
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

690
00:33:44,160 --> 00:33:45,960
[SPEAKER_00] I to je ono što je u stvari pokazalo se.

691
00:33:45,960 --> 00:33:47,740
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ovi roditelji koji su mjeri,

692
00:33:54,619 --> 00:33:56,160
[SPEAKER_00] pokazalo se da su oni sami,

693
00:33:56,160 --> 00:33:57,920
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, na tu mjeru reagirali tako

694
00:33:57,920 --> 00:33:59,420
[SPEAKER_00] da su imali još djece,

695
00:33:59,420 --> 00:34:00,880
[SPEAKER_00] a da nisu isto vremeno,

696
00:34:00,880 --> 00:34:02,160
[SPEAKER_00] ta djeca je išla u vrtiće,

697
00:34:02,160 --> 00:34:03,380
[SPEAKER_00] otteretili su vrtiće.

698
00:34:03,380 --> 00:34:05,599
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, rekla bih da iz ove mjera

699
00:34:05,599 --> 00:34:09,659
[SPEAKER_00] koju se pogleda sa jednim objektivnim pogledom

700
00:34:09,659 --> 00:34:11,860
[SPEAKER_00] smo doista naučili puno toga.

701
00:34:11,860 --> 00:34:13,500
[SPEAKER_00] Upravo ovo što si rekao

702
00:34:13,500 --> 00:34:15,619
[SPEAKER_00] o toj otpornosti obitelji

703
00:34:15,619 --> 00:34:17,519
[SPEAKER_00] koje već imaju troje djece.

704
00:34:17,519 --> 00:34:19,019
[SPEAKER_00] I u konačnici, nekako,

705
00:34:19,019 --> 00:34:21,179
[SPEAKER_00] ja imam dojam i u razgovorima

706
00:34:21,179 --> 00:34:22,519
[SPEAKER_00] s puno roditelja oko sad,

707
00:34:22,519 --> 00:34:23,960
[SPEAKER_00] i te mjere sam razgovarila,

708
00:34:24,079 --> 00:34:25,760
[SPEAKER_00] imam dojam da na neki način

709
00:34:25,760 --> 00:34:26,960
[SPEAKER_00] ti sam shvatiš

710
00:34:26,960 --> 00:34:28,639
[SPEAKER_00] kad dobiješ to treće djete.

711
00:34:28,639 --> 00:34:30,840
[SPEAKER_00] Shvatiš da to možeš.

712
00:34:30,840 --> 00:34:33,519
[SPEAKER_01] Jako mogu još samo jednu rečenicu

713
00:34:33,519 --> 00:34:34,039
[SPEAKER_01] oko te mjere,

714
00:34:34,039 --> 00:34:37,400
[SPEAKER_01] pa da ne idemo previše tu piču širiti.

715
00:34:37,400 --> 00:34:39,679
[SPEAKER_01] Često puca se možda neki roditelji

716
00:34:39,679 --> 00:34:40,539
[SPEAKER_01] koji tu mjeru koriste

717
00:34:40,539 --> 00:34:42,579
[SPEAKER_01] i neopravdano etiketiraju

718
00:34:42,579 --> 00:34:43,679
[SPEAKER_01] škoro da kažem napadaj.

719
00:34:43,679 --> 00:34:44,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ta mjera je dobrovoljna.

720
00:34:44,920 --> 00:34:46,679
[SPEAKER_01] Odnosno, nemaju svi roditelji.

721
00:34:46,679 --> 00:34:47,460
[SPEAKER_01] Stroje ili više djece,

722
00:34:47,460 --> 00:34:48,619
[SPEAKER_01] govorim samo u gradu Zagrebu,

723
00:34:48,619 --> 00:34:50,260
[SPEAKER_01] ja osobno nisam sa rovnik grada Zagreba,

724
00:34:50,420 --> 00:34:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] tako da nemam s to mjere nikakvog dodira

725
00:34:53,000 --> 00:34:54,860
[SPEAKER_01] osobno, ali to je pitanje

726
00:34:54,860 --> 00:34:55,559
[SPEAKER_01] osobnog izbora.

727
00:34:55,559 --> 00:34:57,300
[SPEAKER_01] Nekim roditeljima to odgovara,

728
00:34:57,300 --> 00:34:58,699
[SPEAKER_01] nekima ne, nekima odgovara

729
00:34:58,699 --> 00:34:59,900
[SPEAKER_01] da tu mjeru koriste do, ne znam,

730
00:34:59,900 --> 00:35:01,860
[SPEAKER_01] osme godine života nemalog djeteta,

731
00:35:01,860 --> 00:35:03,360
[SPEAKER_01] nekog malo duže, nekog kraće.

732
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:04,480
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je ono što,

733
00:35:04,480 --> 00:35:06,300
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, nikog se time ništa ne prisiljava.

734
00:35:06,960 --> 00:35:08,619
[SPEAKER_01] I to je ono što se, evo, često puta čini mi se

735
00:35:08,619 --> 00:35:09,679
[SPEAKER_01] u tom medijskom prostoru,

736
00:35:09,679 --> 00:35:11,219
[SPEAKER_01] u simovim raspravama oko te mjere

737
00:35:11,219 --> 00:35:12,460
[SPEAKER_01] isto zanimarivalo.

738
00:35:12,460 --> 00:35:14,179
[SPEAKER_01] Ispalo je koda svako ko ima više djece

739
00:35:14,179 --> 00:35:15,679
[SPEAKER_01] nužno mora koristiti tu mjeru,

740
00:35:15,679 --> 00:35:17,039
[SPEAKER_01] pa se, ne znam, maknice svog posla

741
00:35:17,039 --> 00:35:17,760
[SPEAKER_01] i takle, ne, ne.

742
00:35:17,760 --> 00:35:20,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, niti je to ideja,

743
00:35:20,820 --> 00:35:22,920
[SPEAKER_00] niti je to u konačnici grad Zagrebi

744
00:35:22,920 --> 00:35:25,119
[SPEAKER_00] 2016. godine, kad je uveo mjeru,

745
00:35:25,119 --> 00:35:26,519
[SPEAKER_00] je na kuć, na adrese ljudi

746
00:35:26,519 --> 00:35:28,659
[SPEAKER_00] koji su tada imali troje i više djece,

747
00:35:28,659 --> 00:35:30,800
[SPEAKER_00] poslao, objasnio

748
00:35:30,800 --> 00:35:32,019
[SPEAKER_00] koje su mogućnosti

749
00:35:32,019 --> 00:35:33,500
[SPEAKER_00] i pitao da li vi želite u nju ući.

750
00:35:33,500 --> 00:35:35,519
[SPEAKER_00] Prema tome, tko je želio ušo,

751
00:35:35,519 --> 00:35:37,599
[SPEAKER_00] tko želi, može svaki tren izaći iz nje.

752
00:35:37,599 --> 00:35:40,059
[SPEAKER_00] Prema tome, to je sad stvar dogovora roditelja

753
00:35:40,059 --> 00:35:42,159
[SPEAKER_00] kako oni vide da oni najbolje mogu organizirati.

754
00:35:42,159 --> 00:35:45,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ali meni se jako sviđa mogućnost

755
00:35:45,300 --> 00:35:47,980
[SPEAKER_00] da ljudi mogu, da se ljudima omogući

756
00:35:47,980 --> 00:35:51,039
[SPEAKER_00] da odaberu i da se vredno je njihov rad.

757
00:35:51,039 --> 00:35:53,539
[SPEAKER_00] Dobro si rekao da su roditelji, odgojitelji

758
00:35:53,539 --> 00:35:56,639
[SPEAKER_00] bili izloženi od određenog dijela

759
00:35:56,639 --> 00:35:58,460
[SPEAKER_00] političara i javnosti.

760
00:35:58,460 --> 00:36:00,019
[SPEAKER_00] Na njih se napadalo.

761
00:36:00,840 --> 00:36:03,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ja moram reći da jedan dio ljudi

762
00:36:03,780 --> 00:36:06,480
[SPEAKER_00] ih je napadao, ja bih se usudila

763
00:36:06,480 --> 00:36:07,579
[SPEAKER_00] reći iz zavisti.

764
00:36:07,579 --> 00:36:09,420
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, zato jer mi se,

765
00:36:09,420 --> 00:36:13,980
[SPEAKER_00] kao u stilu, ja nisam to mogao koristiti,

766
00:36:13,980 --> 00:36:17,480
[SPEAKER_00] jer nisam, do 2016. nije bilo te mjere,

767
00:36:17,480 --> 00:36:19,360
[SPEAKER_00] zašto bi njima bilo lakše?

768
00:36:19,360 --> 00:36:20,400
[SPEAKER_00] Pa zašto ne?

769
00:36:20,400 --> 00:36:23,559
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nek bude barem nekome malo lakše

770
00:36:23,559 --> 00:36:24,719
[SPEAKER_00] i malo bolje.

771
00:36:24,719 --> 00:36:26,900
[SPEAKER_00] Prema tome, a u konačnici,

772
00:36:26,900 --> 00:36:28,900
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam sigurna da ako sam,

773
00:36:29,500 --> 00:36:32,760
[SPEAKER_00] jedino ulaganje za koje sam sigurna da se uvijek isplati

774
00:36:32,760 --> 00:36:34,079
[SPEAKER_00] je ulaganje u ljude.

775
00:36:34,079 --> 00:36:34,559
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

776
00:36:34,559 --> 00:36:35,320
[SPEAKER_00] Je ulaganje u ljude.

777
00:36:35,320 --> 00:36:36,320
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si,

778
00:36:36,320 --> 00:36:38,239
[SPEAKER_00] jedan od važnijih projekata,

779
00:36:38,239 --> 00:36:41,780
[SPEAKER_00] stvari o kojoj se vi zalažete i borite su

780
00:36:41,780 --> 00:36:43,239
[SPEAKER_00] obiteljske kartice.

781
00:36:43,239 --> 00:36:46,079
[SPEAKER_01] Obiteljske kartice je praktički temeljni,

782
00:36:46,079 --> 00:36:47,739
[SPEAKER_01] mi kažemo, bazni projekt naše udruge

783
00:36:47,739 --> 00:36:49,420
[SPEAKER_01] i zapravo već kad smo osnivali udrugu,

784
00:36:49,420 --> 00:36:51,019
[SPEAKER_01] smo dobili te preporuke,

785
00:36:51,019 --> 00:36:52,079
[SPEAKER_01] to nismo mi izmislili,

786
00:36:52,079 --> 00:36:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] dobili smo preporuke

787
00:36:53,000 --> 00:36:55,699
[SPEAKER_01] iz drugih naših sestrinskih organizacija,

788
00:36:55,699 --> 00:36:56,780
[SPEAKER_01] iz drugih zemalja Evrope,

789
00:36:56,780 --> 00:36:58,539
[SPEAKER_01] od Poljske, Špaljnovske, Italije itd.

790
00:36:58,539 --> 00:37:01,260
[SPEAKER_01] Njemačke, gdje takve obiteljske kartice postoje.

791
00:37:01,260 --> 00:37:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Što je obiteljske kartice?

792
00:37:03,000 --> 00:37:05,300
[SPEAKER_01] To je dakle jedna loyalty kartica,

793
00:37:05,300 --> 00:37:05,820
[SPEAKER_01] možemo reći,

794
00:37:05,820 --> 00:37:07,079
[SPEAKER_01] namenjena našim članovima,

795
00:37:07,079 --> 00:37:09,519
[SPEAKER_01] dakle obiteljima stroje ili više djece,

796
00:37:09,519 --> 00:37:11,099
[SPEAKER_01] kojima naši članovi,

797
00:37:11,099 --> 00:37:12,539
[SPEAKER_01] kod naših partnera,

798
00:37:12,539 --> 00:37:13,920
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno partnerskih poduzeća,

799
00:37:13,920 --> 00:37:16,260
[SPEAKER_01] sadljenih od 90-ak u našoj mreži,

800
00:37:16,260 --> 00:37:18,260
[SPEAKER_01] onda ostvaruju određene pogodnosti,

801
00:37:18,260 --> 00:37:20,639
[SPEAKER_01] popuste pri kupnji proizvoda

802
00:37:20,639 --> 00:37:21,880
[SPEAKER_01] ili usluga tih partnera.

803
00:37:21,880 --> 00:37:24,059
[SPEAKER_01] Koji se kreću od postotka,

804
00:37:24,059 --> 00:37:25,179
[SPEAKER_01] bilo na neki drugi način,

805
00:37:25,179 --> 00:37:27,719
[SPEAKER_01] ima tu i ono baš konkretnih

806
00:37:27,719 --> 00:37:29,340
[SPEAKER_01] i značajnijih popusta

807
00:37:29,340 --> 00:37:31,400
[SPEAKER_01] i to na kupnju razno raznih proizvoda

808
00:37:31,400 --> 00:37:33,239
[SPEAKER_01] od nekih prehrambenih artikala

809
00:37:33,239 --> 00:37:34,059
[SPEAKER_01] do automobila,

810
00:37:34,059 --> 00:37:37,019
[SPEAKER_01] telekomunikacijih usluga,

811
00:37:37,019 --> 00:37:39,400
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam, smještaja u hotelima,

812
00:37:39,400 --> 00:37:40,699
[SPEAKER_01] restoranima, kafićima,

813
00:37:40,699 --> 00:37:42,099
[SPEAKER_01] ne kafićima, restoranima,

814
00:37:42,099 --> 00:37:44,739
[SPEAKER_01] i tako dalje.

815
00:37:44,739 --> 00:37:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, stvarno imamo cijelu lepezu

816
00:37:47,000 --> 00:37:49,719
[SPEAKER_01] partnera iz razno raznim djelatnosti.

817
00:37:49,719 --> 00:37:50,860
[SPEAKER_01] Ja i ovom prilikom pozivam

818
00:37:50,860 --> 00:37:52,539
[SPEAKER_01] evo sve vas, poduzetnike,

819
00:37:52,539 --> 00:37:54,440
[SPEAKER_01] sve vas koji imate neku moć

820
00:37:54,440 --> 00:37:55,659
[SPEAKER_01] u odlučivanju nekom poduzeću,

821
00:37:55,659 --> 00:37:56,840
[SPEAKER_01] ako je nudi neki proizvod

822
00:37:56,840 --> 00:37:58,719
[SPEAKER_01] ili uslugu za obitelji,

823
00:37:58,719 --> 00:37:59,840
[SPEAKER_01] da nam se javite

824
00:37:59,840 --> 00:38:01,320
[SPEAKER_01] i da onda uspostavamo suradnju,

825
00:38:01,400 --> 00:38:02,219
[SPEAKER_01] i da na taj način

826
00:38:02,219 --> 00:38:03,639
[SPEAKER_01] i vi kao poslodavci pokažete

827
00:38:03,639 --> 00:38:06,099
[SPEAKER_01] podršku velikim obiteljima.

828
00:38:06,099 --> 00:38:07,559
[SPEAKER_01] I to stvarno super funkcionira,

829
00:38:07,559 --> 00:38:08,739
[SPEAKER_01] ali to je jedna, evo,

830
00:38:08,739 --> 00:38:09,519
[SPEAKER_01] s sve strane,

831
00:38:09,519 --> 00:38:11,500
[SPEAKER_01] konkretan znak pažnje,

832
00:38:11,500 --> 00:38:12,659
[SPEAKER_01] mogu reći, poslodavaca,

833
00:38:12,659 --> 00:38:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] znači, realnog sektora,

834
00:38:14,000 --> 00:38:16,119
[SPEAKER_01] da pokazuje koliko su im

835
00:38:16,119 --> 00:38:17,480
[SPEAKER_01] obitelji sviše djece važne.

836
00:38:17,480 --> 00:38:18,719
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, naša uloga nije

837
00:38:18,719 --> 00:38:19,579
[SPEAKER_01] samo ovdje u društvu,

838
00:38:19,579 --> 00:38:20,039
[SPEAKER_01] kao u druge,

839
00:38:20,039 --> 00:38:23,199
[SPEAKER_01] da senzibiliziramo javne politike,

840
00:38:23,199 --> 00:38:24,860
[SPEAKER_01] nego i ovaj privatni,

841
00:38:24,860 --> 00:38:25,579
[SPEAKER_01] realni sektor,

842
00:38:25,579 --> 00:38:26,699
[SPEAKER_01] da je on je delo svoj podršku,

843
00:38:26,780 --> 00:38:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] evo, kažem ja ovim putem stvarno,

844
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:30,739
[SPEAKER_01] svima koji već su delili u tom programu,

845
00:38:30,739 --> 00:38:32,519
[SPEAKER_01] a tu su neke velike nacionalne firme,

846
00:38:32,519 --> 00:38:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] da sad nijedno ne ističem posebno,

847
00:38:34,000 --> 00:38:37,239
[SPEAKER_01] evo, mogu ipak jedno istaknuti,

848
00:38:37,239 --> 00:38:38,139
[SPEAKER_01] recimo Hrvatska,

849
00:38:38,139 --> 00:38:39,480
[SPEAKER_01] HEP Opskrba.

850
00:38:39,480 --> 00:38:40,840
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, svi naši članovi

851
00:38:40,840 --> 00:38:42,280
[SPEAKER_01] mogu preko HEP Opskrbe,

852
00:38:42,280 --> 00:38:43,380
[SPEAKER_01] to je dakle jedna uslova

853
00:38:43,380 --> 00:38:44,360
[SPEAKER_01] koja je stvarno svima dostupna,

854
00:38:44,360 --> 00:38:45,719
[SPEAKER_01] dobiti jeftiniju struju,

855
00:38:45,719 --> 00:38:48,039
[SPEAKER_01] jeftiniju cijenu električne energije.

856
00:38:48,039 --> 00:38:49,619
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da to je recimo nešto

857
00:38:49,619 --> 00:38:51,780
[SPEAKER_01] što je onda svaki mjesec

858
00:38:51,780 --> 00:38:52,780
[SPEAKER_01] malo pozdrav na računu,

859
00:38:52,780 --> 00:38:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer mislim to je vrlo konkretna stavka

860
00:38:57,000 --> 00:38:58,639
[SPEAKER_01] u proračunu svakog domačina,

861
00:38:58,639 --> 00:39:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] svaka je tri plus domačinstva,

862
00:39:01,000 --> 00:39:02,519
