1062
00:44:28,320 --> 00:44:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, pa imaš preskupi račun,

1063
00:44:30,000 --> 00:44:32,099
[SPEAKER_01] prebi kredit s ovim, ne znam,

1064
00:44:32,099 --> 00:44:33,980
[SPEAKER_01] ovo, ono, ulaganje, napravi tamo, ne znam.

1065
00:44:33,980 --> 00:44:34,719
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

1066
00:44:34,719 --> 00:44:36,860
[SPEAKER_00] Netko ima smisla za to, netko nema.

1067
00:44:36,860 --> 00:44:39,159
[SPEAKER_01] Tako, evo, to su sad samo jedan od primjera

1068
00:44:39,159 --> 00:44:41,360
[SPEAKER_01] koje mi naostavimo pokrenuti,

1069
00:44:41,360 --> 00:44:42,059
[SPEAKER_01] koji smo pokrenuli.

1070
00:44:42,059 --> 00:44:43,679
[SPEAKER_01] Biće tak i, nadam, se inicijativa

1071
00:44:43,679 --> 00:44:45,159
[SPEAKER_01] sve više i više s naše strane

1072
00:44:45,159 --> 00:44:47,639
[SPEAKER_01] i zapravo nam je cilj da

1073
00:44:47,639 --> 00:44:49,960
[SPEAKER_01] u ovoj godini

1074
00:44:49,960 --> 00:44:52,099
[SPEAKER_01] osnovimo županijske područnice

1075
00:44:52,099 --> 00:44:53,119
[SPEAKER_01] na županijskoj razini

1076
00:44:53,119 --> 00:44:54,780
[SPEAKER_01] kako bi naše članove

1077
00:44:54,780 --> 00:44:56,579
[SPEAKER_01] imali priliku

1078
00:44:56,579 --> 00:44:58,179
[SPEAKER_01] i sada fizički onako okupiti.

1079
00:44:58,179 --> 00:44:59,400
[SPEAKER_01] To smo mislili već i prije,

1080
00:44:59,400 --> 00:45:00,780
[SPEAKER_01] a nas je ova korona, naravno,

1081
00:45:00,780 --> 00:45:01,519
[SPEAKER_01] kao i mnoga druge,

1082
00:45:01,519 --> 00:45:03,219
[SPEAKER_01] u svemu omela i zaostavila.

1083
00:45:03,219 --> 00:45:05,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, evo, stvarno vjerujemo

1084
00:45:05,019 --> 00:45:06,219
[SPEAKER_01] da će ove godine to biti moguće

1085
00:45:06,219 --> 00:45:08,340
[SPEAKER_01] i naše članstvo je sad već poprilično veliko,

1086
00:45:08,340 --> 00:45:09,699
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda svaka županija

1087
00:45:09,699 --> 00:45:11,699
[SPEAKER_01] ima stvarno već puno, puno, puno članova

1088
00:45:11,699 --> 00:45:14,719
[SPEAKER_01] i da onda kroz konkretne susrete

1089
00:45:14,719 --> 00:45:17,119
[SPEAKER_01] koji će nekad biti žernijeg tipa,

1090
00:45:17,119 --> 00:45:18,039
[SPEAKER_01] neki izlet i tako dalje,

1091
00:45:18,099 --> 00:45:20,019
[SPEAKER_01] a nekad će biti edukativni i sl.

1092
00:45:20,019 --> 00:45:22,179
[SPEAKER_01] Da onda stvarno snažujemo jedni druge.

1093
00:45:22,179 --> 00:45:25,099
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da, zašto bi svaka obitelj

1094
00:45:25,099 --> 00:45:27,679
[SPEAKER_00] kretala iz početka učeći?

1095
00:45:27,679 --> 00:45:29,800
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto ne bi, evo, jedni od drugih

1096
00:45:29,800 --> 00:45:31,539
[SPEAKER_00] prenoseći znanje

1097
00:45:31,539 --> 00:45:34,079
[SPEAKER_00] u tim specifičnim okolnostima

1098
00:45:34,079 --> 00:45:36,440
[SPEAKER_00] pomicali se prema napred?

1099
00:45:36,440 --> 00:45:38,940
[SPEAKER_00] I ono što nekako se meni čini

1100
00:45:38,940 --> 00:45:41,300
[SPEAKER_00] i da ne zaboravimo

1101
00:45:41,300 --> 00:45:42,800
[SPEAKER_00] stalno jedni druge pocijećati

1102
00:45:42,800 --> 00:45:45,420
[SPEAKER_00] da u sve te obaveze,

1103
00:45:45,420 --> 00:45:46,880
[SPEAKER_00] financijske probleme,

1104
00:45:47,420 --> 00:45:48,760
[SPEAKER_00] sve ovo što si rekao,

1105
00:45:48,760 --> 00:45:50,900
[SPEAKER_00] koordinacija, organizacija,

1106
00:45:50,900 --> 00:45:52,440
[SPEAKER_00] da ne izgubimo iz videa

1107
00:45:52,440 --> 00:45:53,219
[SPEAKER_00] koliko je to super.

1108
00:45:53,219 --> 00:45:55,599
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko je to super imati djece,

1109
00:45:55,599 --> 00:46:00,119
[SPEAKER_00] koliko želi da i s drugima to podijelimo.

1110
00:46:00,119 --> 00:46:01,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bih rekao, to je jedan vrlo ozbiljan posao

1111
00:46:01,840 --> 00:46:03,039
[SPEAKER_01] u kojem se mi jako dobro zabavljamo.

1112
00:46:03,039 --> 00:46:04,940
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, u kojem se jako dobro zabavljamo.

1113
00:46:04,940 --> 00:46:05,900
[SPEAKER_00] Mi i djeca,

1114
00:46:05,900 --> 00:46:06,960
[SPEAKER_01] a odnosno ako to nije tako,

1115
00:46:06,960 --> 00:46:08,019
[SPEAKER_01] onda nešto nešto ima u poslu.

1116
00:46:08,019 --> 00:46:08,820
[SPEAKER_00] Nešto nešto ima.

1117
00:46:08,820 --> 00:46:10,579
[SPEAKER_00] Nije dobro nešto ako nam svima nije

1118
00:46:10,579 --> 00:46:12,340
[SPEAKER_00] na kraju dobro.

1119
00:46:12,340 --> 00:46:14,019
[SPEAKER_00] Jer naravno da u svemu ima,

1120
00:46:14,119 --> 00:46:16,119
[SPEAKER_00] u procesu imam poteškoća u svakome.

1121
00:46:16,119 --> 00:46:18,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ali zanimljivo je to da u današnje vrijeme,

1122
00:46:18,960 --> 00:46:22,380
[SPEAKER_00] kada u stvari će svatko u javnosti ko govori,

1123
00:46:22,380 --> 00:46:25,119
[SPEAKER_00] 99% tih poruka će biti o tome

1124
00:46:25,119 --> 00:46:27,199
[SPEAKER_00] kako su ljudi najveća vrijednost,

1125
00:46:27,199 --> 00:46:29,539
[SPEAKER_00] kako najveće bogatstvo su ljudski odnosi,

1126
00:46:29,539 --> 00:46:30,599
[SPEAKER_00] nisu važne stvari,

1127
00:46:30,599 --> 00:46:31,480
[SPEAKER_00] važni su ljudi.

1128
00:46:31,940 --> 00:46:34,480
[SPEAKER_00] I sve to je istina,

1129
00:46:34,480 --> 00:46:36,059
[SPEAKER_00] ali onda kada dođe do toga,

1130
00:46:36,059 --> 00:46:37,679
[SPEAKER_00] pa s kim to imamo odnosi,

1131
00:46:37,679 --> 00:46:39,960
[SPEAKER_00] ko su ti ljudi koji su najvažniji,

1132
00:46:39,960 --> 00:46:41,559
[SPEAKER_00] onda se ta slika gubi.

1133
00:46:41,559 --> 00:46:44,599
[SPEAKER_00] I na neki način stvaraju se ti stereotipi

1134
00:46:44,599 --> 00:46:46,840
[SPEAKER_00] i u Hrvatskoj se to moglo u nekoliko navrata,

1135
00:46:46,840 --> 00:46:48,739
[SPEAKER_00] u više navrata, nažalost, prepoznati,

1136
00:46:48,739 --> 00:46:50,739
[SPEAKER_00] kao da su one obitelji koje imaju djecu,

1137
00:46:50,739 --> 00:46:52,260
[SPEAKER_00] imaju da su siromašne,

1138
00:46:52,260 --> 00:46:53,559
[SPEAKER_00] da su neobrazovani,

1139
00:46:53,559 --> 00:46:54,940
[SPEAKER_00] da im...

1140
00:46:55,739 --> 00:46:57,179
[SPEAKER_00] I mi smo se isto kao udruga,

1141
00:46:57,179 --> 00:46:58,820
[SPEAKER_00] i vaša se udruga angažirila oko onog,

1142
00:46:58,820 --> 00:47:01,619
[SPEAKER_00] ono jedne ilustracije gdje je prikazana obitelj s djecom

1143
00:47:01,619 --> 00:47:03,780
[SPEAKER_00] ko da nisu normalni,

1144
00:47:03,780 --> 00:47:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] ni majka, ni ti otac.

1145
00:47:05,000 --> 00:47:08,699
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ti nekakvi, u stvari, projekcije ljudi

1146
00:47:08,699 --> 00:47:11,719
[SPEAKER_00] koji možda ne poznaju obitelji sa više djece

1147
00:47:11,719 --> 00:47:12,860
[SPEAKER_00] ili predrasude,

1148
00:47:12,860 --> 00:47:16,460
[SPEAKER_00] vi se isto borite time da se to smanji.

1149
00:47:16,460 --> 00:47:18,219
[SPEAKER_01] Je, to je još jedan od naših ciljeva,

1150
00:47:18,219 --> 00:47:20,900
[SPEAKER_01] da bažda se te predrasude i stereotipi,

1151
00:47:20,900 --> 00:47:22,679
[SPEAKER_01] a posebno negativni,

1152
00:47:22,679 --> 00:47:25,699
[SPEAKER_01] koji nema opravdanje obiteljima s više djece,

1153
00:47:25,739 --> 00:47:28,539
[SPEAKER_01] da se ti stereotipi razbiju,

1154
00:47:28,539 --> 00:47:30,340
[SPEAKER_01] da se, da kažem, unište.

1155
00:47:30,340 --> 00:47:33,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bih se još malo osvrnuo na ovo istraživanje

1156
00:47:33,539 --> 00:47:34,320
[SPEAKER_01] koje si ti spominjala.

1157
00:47:34,320 --> 00:47:35,420
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, riječ o jednom istraživanju

1158
00:47:35,420 --> 00:47:37,980
[SPEAKER_01] koje je provala jedna znanstvena skupina

1159
00:47:37,980 --> 00:47:39,519
[SPEAKER_01] s jednog hrvatskog slučilišta,

1160
00:47:39,519 --> 00:47:42,340
[SPEAKER_01] čiji rezultati su predstavljeni u našim javnim medijima,

1161
00:47:42,340 --> 00:47:43,539
[SPEAKER_01] a onda su pojedine mediji,

1162
00:47:43,539 --> 00:47:45,239
[SPEAKER_01] konkretno mislim sad na jedne dnevne novine,

1163
00:47:45,239 --> 00:47:47,340
[SPEAKER_01] samo inicijativno,

1164
00:47:47,340 --> 00:47:49,280
[SPEAKER_01] uz rezultata tog istraživanja

1165
00:47:49,280 --> 00:47:50,980
[SPEAKER_01] u kojima se uopće ne spominja obitelj,

1166
00:47:50,980 --> 00:47:51,940
[SPEAKER_01] a kamali obitelj s djecom,

1167
00:47:52,320 --> 00:47:54,539
[SPEAKER_01] su napravili, dakle, određene ilustracije

1168
00:47:54,539 --> 00:47:56,739
[SPEAKER_01] koje su bilo vredljive,

1169
00:47:56,739 --> 00:47:58,119
[SPEAKER_01] konkretno radi se o istraživanju

1170
00:47:58,119 --> 00:48:00,699
[SPEAKER_01] o statusnim ili klasnim razlikama Hrvata,

1171
00:48:00,699 --> 00:48:02,820
[SPEAKER_01] gdje su onda građani strpani,

1172
00:48:02,820 --> 00:48:05,059
[SPEAKER_01] odnos, svrstani u četiri kategorije,

1173
00:48:05,059 --> 00:48:07,360
[SPEAKER_01] neke niža klasa, srednja klasa,

1174
00:48:07,360 --> 00:48:08,559
[SPEAKER_01] radnička i, ne znam, elita.

1175
00:48:08,559 --> 00:48:11,340
[SPEAKER_01] I onda je, dakle, to prikazano nekom piramidom,

1176
00:48:11,340 --> 00:48:12,579
[SPEAKER_01] gdje su sad, ne znam,

1177
00:48:12,579 --> 00:48:15,079
[SPEAKER_01] na najniže klasi prikazane

1178
00:48:15,079 --> 00:48:16,199
[SPEAKER_01] dva umirovljenika,

1179
00:48:16,199 --> 00:48:18,039
[SPEAKER_01] baka i djetko i tamo, onda,

1180
00:48:18,039 --> 00:48:20,139
[SPEAKER_01] jedna krba u kraju s krajem,

1181
00:48:20,280 --> 00:48:22,119
[SPEAKER_01] i kraj njih jedna obitelj,

1182
00:48:22,119 --> 00:48:23,480
[SPEAKER_01] gdje mama i tata,

1183
00:48:23,480 --> 00:48:25,280
[SPEAKER_01] i oko njih petro djece u rukama

1184
00:48:25,280 --> 00:48:26,559
[SPEAKER_01] i oko njih od njih rastežu,

1185
00:48:26,559 --> 00:48:27,719
[SPEAKER_01] mama je sva čupava,

1186
00:48:27,719 --> 00:48:28,780
[SPEAKER_01] to je onak ilustracijansko,

1187
00:48:28,780 --> 00:48:30,159
[SPEAKER_01] ali sve se vidi čupava je,

1188
00:48:30,159 --> 00:48:31,840
[SPEAKER_01] tužni čovakavi kod nje,

1189
00:48:31,840 --> 00:48:33,280
[SPEAKER_01] kod tate, ono, ajme meni,

1190
00:48:33,280 --> 00:48:34,059
[SPEAKER_01] šta me ovo trebalo,

1191
00:48:34,059 --> 00:48:35,900
[SPEAKER_01] ovih razlača kora su zadnji patnici,

1192
00:48:35,900 --> 00:48:38,519
[SPEAKER_01] a ovi svi gore se jako super zabavljaju.

1193
00:48:38,519 --> 00:48:39,139
[SPEAKER_01] Njima je super.

1194
00:48:39,139 --> 00:48:40,940
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, znači, s kojim pravom je

1195
00:48:40,940 --> 00:48:43,179
[SPEAKER_01] ta niža klasa prikazana na ovakav način?

1196
00:48:43,260 --> 00:48:45,519
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo, dakle, ponukani upravo tim istraživanjem

1197
00:48:45,519 --> 00:48:46,440
[SPEAKER_01] Udraga obitelji 3+,

1198
00:48:46,440 --> 00:48:47,659
[SPEAKER_01] provovalo jedno veliko istraživanje

1199
00:48:47,659 --> 00:48:50,039
[SPEAKER_01] na skoro tisuć i pol ispitanika,

1200
00:48:50,039 --> 00:48:52,619
[SPEAKER_01] gdje smo zapravo ispitali

1201
00:48:52,619 --> 00:48:54,059
[SPEAKER_01] u baš obitelji stola više djece,

1202
00:48:54,059 --> 00:48:56,179
[SPEAKER_01] kako je njihovo stanje vezano

1203
00:48:56,179 --> 00:48:58,699
[SPEAKER_01] uz statusne te klasne razlike,

1204
00:48:58,699 --> 00:49:00,380
[SPEAKER_01] pri čemu smo upotrebili

1205
00:49:00,380 --> 00:49:01,340
[SPEAKER_01] otprilike ista pitanja

1206
00:49:01,340 --> 00:49:02,719
[SPEAKER_01] kao i ovo originalno istraživanje.

1207
00:49:02,719 --> 00:49:04,179
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, tu se ne govori samo o tome

1208
00:49:04,179 --> 00:49:05,639
[SPEAKER_01] koliko od koji ima sredstava

1209
00:49:05,639 --> 00:49:06,480
[SPEAKER_01] na tekućem računu,

1210
00:49:06,480 --> 00:49:10,619
[SPEAKER_01] nego taj statusni odnosno klasni razred

1211
00:49:10,619 --> 00:49:13,099
[SPEAKER_01] ovisi i opropo znanstava, prijatelja,

1212
00:49:13,099 --> 00:49:14,800
[SPEAKER_01] obrazovanja i tako dalje,

1213
00:49:14,800 --> 00:49:17,119
[SPEAKER_01] kogu knjiga imate doma i tako dalje.

1214
00:49:17,119 --> 00:49:18,500
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, kad smo sve to uzeli obzir,

1215
00:49:18,500 --> 00:49:21,239
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, mi smo utvrdili da naša struktura

1216
00:49:21,239 --> 00:49:23,199
[SPEAKER_01] 3+, obitelji zapravo po svemu prati

1217
00:49:23,199 --> 00:49:24,679
[SPEAKER_01] strukturu i običajnog,

1218
00:49:24,679 --> 00:49:26,219
[SPEAKER_01] običajnog hrvatske obitelji,

1219
00:49:26,219 --> 00:49:28,179
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, nipo čemu mi ne zaostajemo,

1220
00:49:28,179 --> 00:49:30,059
[SPEAKER_01] mislim na 3+, obitelji

1221
00:49:30,059 --> 00:49:31,260
[SPEAKER_01] i meni je izvjetno drago što,

1222
00:49:31,260 --> 00:49:34,039
[SPEAKER_01] ja vidim dakle, naši članovi pod njima vidim,

1223
00:49:34,440 --> 00:49:36,059
[SPEAKER_01] stvarno jako puno imamo obitelji

1224
00:49:36,059 --> 00:49:37,739
[SPEAKER_01] koji su po svemu raznolike,

1225
00:49:37,739 --> 00:49:39,579
[SPEAKER_01] ali stvarno imamo jako puno

1226
00:49:39,579 --> 00:49:41,699
[SPEAKER_01] i visokoobrazovnih ljudi i poduzetnika

1227
00:49:41,699 --> 00:49:44,300
[SPEAKER_01] i, znači, ljudi će djeca

1228
00:49:44,300 --> 00:49:45,760
[SPEAKER_01] postavaju u prva mjesta

1229
00:49:45,760 --> 00:49:47,980
[SPEAKER_01] čime god se bave i tako dalje.

1230
00:49:47,980 --> 00:49:49,699
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da nema nikakve razlike

1231
00:49:49,699 --> 00:49:52,059
[SPEAKER_01] u smislu, načalno, da su ta djeca

1232
00:49:52,059 --> 00:49:54,320
[SPEAKER_01] ili roditelji pametniji ili manje pametni

1233
00:49:54,320 --> 00:49:56,900
[SPEAKER_01] i mučni obrazovani ili manje obrazovani,

1234
00:49:56,900 --> 00:49:58,679
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, to nema nikakve razlike.

1235
00:49:58,679 --> 00:50:01,360
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, u stvari, obitelji sa troje i više djece

1236
00:50:01,360 --> 00:50:03,280
[SPEAKER_00] imaju sličnu distribuciju

1237
00:50:03,280 --> 00:50:05,280
[SPEAKER_00] unutar tih klasa

1238
00:50:05,280 --> 00:50:07,800
[SPEAKER_00] koje su podijeljene, kao i druge obitelji,

1239
00:50:07,800 --> 00:50:08,960
[SPEAKER_00] drugi ljudi, prema tome.

1240
00:50:08,960 --> 00:50:11,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, ja mislim da je

1241
00:50:11,820 --> 00:50:13,219
[SPEAKER_00] jako važno

1242
00:50:13,219 --> 00:50:14,980
[SPEAKER_00] boriti se protiv tih predrasuda.

1243
00:50:14,980 --> 00:50:17,239
[SPEAKER_00] Prvo radi onih obitelji

1244
00:50:17,239 --> 00:50:19,400
[SPEAKER_00] koje već imaju djecu, ali isto tako

1245
00:50:19,400 --> 00:50:21,559
[SPEAKER_00] potrebno je radi mladih, radi novih ljudi.

1246
00:50:21,559 --> 00:50:23,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ti bi, ako tebe stalno, ako ti prikazuju

1247
00:50:23,659 --> 00:50:24,920
[SPEAKER_00] da imati djecu, znači imati

1248
00:50:24,920 --> 00:50:26,599
[SPEAKER_00] rasčupanu kosu i da te oni razvlače.

1249
00:50:26,599 --> 00:50:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] A s druge strane, opet za mene je to pitanje

1250
00:50:30,539 --> 00:50:32,420
[SPEAKER_00] neće htjeti imati djecu

1251
00:50:32,420 --> 00:50:34,559
[SPEAKER_00] i propustit će nešto što je super u životu.

1252
